OL,3,CStadium ban for man who racially
OL,4,Cabused footballer after goal
OL,6,FA man who sent a racist message to a
OL,7,Ffootballer has been banned from every
OL,8,Fstadium in the country for four years.
OL,10,FConnor Butler, now 20, sent Luton Town
OL,11,Fstriker Elijah Adebayo an abusive
OL,12,Fmessage on Instagram in October 2024
OL,13,Fafter he scored against Sunderland.
OL,15,FButler, of Palermo Street, Pallion,
OL,16,Fwas watching the game at home,
OL,17,FNorthumbria Police said.
OL,19,FThe player saw the message and made a
OL,20,Fcomplaint to police, who traced the
OL,21,FInstagram handle back to Butler.
