OL,6,FHe was arrested in February 2025 and
OL,7,Fcharged with sending communication of
OL,8,Fan indecent or offensive nature.
OL,10,FButler admitted the charge at South
OL,11,FTyneside Magistrates' Court in
OL,12,FDecember and was handed a #200 fine
OL,13,Fand court costs.
OL,15,FHe was back to the same court on
OL,16,FMonday 2 February, where he was handed
OL,17,Fa banning order lasting four years,
OL,18,FNorthumbria Police said.
