OL,3,CStadium ban for man who racially
OL,4,Cabused footballer after goal
OL,6,FHe cannot attend any professional or
OL,7,Fsemi-professional game in England and
OL,8,FWales in that period and must not
OL,9,Ftravel abroad for international
OL,10,Fmatches.
OL,12,FAfter the case, Chief Superintendent
OL,13,FMark Hall, football policing lead for
OL,14,FNorthumbria Police, said: "Racist and
OL,15,Fhateful speech has absolutely no place
OL,16,Fin our communities or online, and we
OL,17,Fknow this kind of behaviour isn't
OL,18,Frepresentative of the overwhelming
OL,19,Fmajority of football fans.
