OL,6,F"We'd like to commend the victim in
OL,7,Fthis case for coming forward to
OL,8,Fpolice, and I am grateful for the
OL,9,Frestrictions which are now stringently
OL,10,Fplaced on Butler.
OL,12,F"I hope this reinforces our commitment
OL,13,Fto taking action against anybody who
OL,14,Fcommits this type of crime ` it will
OL,15,Fnot be tolerated and we will do all we
OL,16,Fcan to put perpetrators before the
OL,17,Fcourts."
