OL,6,FA spokesperson for Luton Town said:
OL,7,F"We have become accustomed to our
OL,8,Fplayers and staff receiving abuse
OL,9,Fonline in recent years.
OL,11,F"Sadly, many have become tired of
OL,12,Freporting it, but Elijah has received
OL,13,Fsome form of racial abuse in each of
OL,14,Fthe five years he has been a Luton
OL,15,FTown player and has always felt
OL,16,Fstrongly enough to make statements to
OL,17,Fthe police.
