OL,3,CStadium ban for man who racially
OL,4,Cabused footballer after goal
OL,6,F"This one thankfully has resulted in a
OL,7,Fprosecution and punishment that we
OL,8,Fhope acts as a deterrent to anyone
OL,9,Fthinking they can send abuse in a
OL,10,Fdirect message, or on any form of
OL,11,Fsocial media, and get away with it.
OL,13,F"We stand with Elijah and all victims
OL,14,Fof discrimination, and will continue
OL,15,Fto fight for any of our Luton Town
OL,16,Ffamily who suffers at the fingertips
OL,17,Fof these keyboard criminals."
